landing.head_title: All in one best AI assistant. Free, fast and personalized.
landing.main_title: Nemati AI provides you advanced AI models such as OpenAI o1, GPT-4o, Mistral-small, Claude 3.5, and Gemini 2.0. Enhance your chat experience with our features, generate unique images using artificial intelligence, refine your code in a simulated IDE environment, and enjoy a seamless interaction. Optimize your business processes, enhance efficiency, and drive growth using advanced AI technologies and cutting-edge generative AI (GEN AI) solutions. Additionally, We at Nemati AI offers a mobile app and browser extension, allowing you to access our AI-powered tools anytime, anywhere.

landing.what_is_prompt: What is a Prompt Library? a prompt library serves as a central Prompt Repository offering AI Prompt Templates, Creative AI Prompts, and AI-Powered Prompt Ideas. It functions like an AI Prompt Generator, providing Generative AI Prompts for improved results. With effective AI Prompt Optimization, you’ll consistently produce high-quality, targeted outputs.

api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_seed_description: Random noise seed. Use 0 for a random seed.
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_step_description: Number of diffusion steps to run.
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_width_description: Width of the image to generate, in pixels, in an increment divisible by 64.
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_extras_description: Extra parameters for the text to image model.
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_height_description: Height of the image to generate, in pixels, in an increment divisible by 64.
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_sampler_description: The sampler to use for the diffusion process.
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_cfg_scale_description: The scale of the config file.
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_style_preset_description: The style preset to use for the image.
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_clip_guidance_preset_descr: The clip guidance preset to use for the image.
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_dimentions_description: The dimensions of the image to generate.
api_keys.dall_e_dimentions_description: The dimensions of the image to generate.
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_image_strength_description: How much influence the image has on the diffusion process.
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_mask_image_description: Mask that allows for influence over which pixels are eligible for diffusion and at what strength. Must be the same dimensions as the init_image
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_mask_source_description: The source of the mask image
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_upscale_by_description: The dimension to upscale the image by
api_keys.sd_txt_to_img_upscale_value_description: The value to upscale the image to. Must be between 512 and 4096
